{"type": "article", "id": 24077, "title": "圆形底座和长线条的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-18T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606151754PkRZpCVIiS2YtAfJ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款灯保持了一种简单的几何感，像是圆环和线的结合。一根斜线充当灯管倾斜穿过了圆形的灯座，与桌面保持锐角，在圆形灯座下面扣了一个可移动的环，相当于一个固定位置的基座。圆环是黑色的，与白色的直线灯管构成强烈的对比，突出了点和线条的结合。这款灯可由 APP 控制，目前还没有上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151752FDCfX8hpy4d3NZjb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151753CvQHxWm38awf5sl6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151753H35rAcdxutO19Dpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151753vOupylwSJchxte3C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 249px; width: 375px; left: 526px; top: 1259px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151754oFqPXYe7OrBhJsdH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}